794
01:17:04,989 --> 01:17:11,192
I will not give up any policy that I care about for someone else to give me some policy that they care about.

795
01:17:11,212 --> 01:17:16,494
I am going to vote on the policies I care about based upon what I believe my constituents deserve.

796
01:17:18,055 --> 01:17:25,618
So this is not a quid pro quo for me, and you will have to wait until we actually vote on it to find out how I feel about this particular intersection.

