1686
02:36:39,179 --> 02:36:41,922
And I think the hardest part of that is that we do not have

1687
02:36:43,060 --> 02:36:49,284
other than the voice that we're putting forward and the requests that we're making for information, the city council doesn't have a vote on this.

1688
02:36:49,484 --> 02:36:53,827
City council can't say, no, this isn't happening or no, it has to be delayed.

1689
02:36:55,428 --> 02:36:56,328
It doesn't sit with us.

1690
02:36:56,788 --> 02:37:00,471
So I have a lot of concerns about the way this was rolled out.

1691
02:37:01,591 --> 02:37:04,233
And I don't think, I think, you know, it's been,

1692
